snippet.description:
Buy Zenzizenzic on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/327500/
“Zenzizenzic is a master thesis in bullet-hell twin stick shooting, both from a design and gameplay standpoint.” -Hardcore Gamer 
If you're looking for a fast-paced, adrenaline-infused twin stick bullet hell shoot 'em up and open world roguelike, look no further than Zenzizenzic. Featuring a beautifully abstract art style and a thumping, full throttle soundtrack, it's sure to get your thumbs sweating and your blood pumping.
